                                   <span>i</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span11">
                                    <h4>{{ _('This is how it’s done') }}</h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span12">
                                   <img src="{{ url_for('plugin.mrbeam.static', filename='img/welcome_dialog/connection-option-detail-a-inner.png') }}">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span12">
                                    <p>{{ _('Select WLAN of your Mr Beam.') }}</p>
                                    <p>{{ _('Name: MrBeam-XXXX <br> Password: mrbeamsetup') }}</p>
                                    <p>{{ _('XXXX stands for your specific device name. You can find it on a sticker on the back of your Mr Beam.') }}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="connection-wizard--selected-option-b" class="connection-wizard--selected-option hide">
            <div class="span12">
                <div class="mrb-relative-position">
                    <img src="{{ url_for('plugin.mrbeam.static', filename='img/welcome_dialog/connection-option-detail-b.png') }}">
                    <span class="connection-wizard__span--b mrb-absolute-position"> {{ _('recommended option') }} </span>
                </div>
                <div class="row-fluid connection-wizard--selected-option__div--main-content">
                    <div class="span6 connection-wizard--selected-option__div--main-content-left">
                        <h4>{{ _('Option B: Network cable connection to the router') }}</h4>
                        <p>{{ _('Connect the Mr Beam to the network router via cable. This configuration is particularly stable due to the cable connection.') }}</p>
                        <p class="mrb-bold">{{ _('Attention. Make sure you do NOT plug it into the similar looking connector for your Airfilter system. The connectors are labeled.') }}</p>
                        <p>{{ _('After that you can access your Mr Beam with any computer (<a href=\"https://find.mr-beam.org\" target=\"_blank\">find.mr-beam.org</a>) that is on the same home network.') }}</p>
                        <h5>{{ _('Pros / Cons') }}</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Most stable and easiest way to connect (recommended)') }}</p></li>
                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Accessible from anywhere in your network') }}</p></li>
                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Software updates via your secured home network access') }}</p></li>
                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Support tickets can be sent directly from your Mr Beam') }}</p></li>
                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Access to the entire Mr Beam Design and Material Store') }}</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="span6">
                        <div class="connection-wizard__div--notice">
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span1">
                                   <span>i</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span11">
                                    <h4>{{ _('This is how it’s done') }}</h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span12">
                                   <img src="{{ url_for('plugin.mrbeam.static', filename=_('img/welcome_dialog/connection-option-detail-b-inner-en.png')) }}">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span12">
                                    <p>{{ _('In your Google Chrome browser, enter the URL <a href=\"https://find.mr-beam.org\" target=\"_blank\">find.mr-beam.org</a> and select the name of your Mr Beam.') }}</p>
                                    <p>{{ _('You can find the device name on the stickers on the back of your Mr Beam.') }}</p>
                                    <p>{{ _('You\'re done.') }}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="connection-wizard--selected-option-c" class="connection-wizard--selected-option hide">
        <div class="span12">
                <div class="mrb-relative-position">
                    <img src="{{ url_for('plugin.mrbeam.static', filename='img/welcome_dialog/connection-option-detail-c.png') }}">
                </div>
                <div class="row-fluid connection-wizard--selected-option__div--main-content">
                    <div class="span12">
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span12 connection-wizard--selected-option__div--main-content-left">
                                <div class="row-fluid">
                                    <div class="span6">
                                        <h4>{{ _('Option C: WiFi connection to the router') }}</h4>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row-fluid">
                                    <div class="span6">
                                        <p>{{ _('Connect Mr Beam via WiFi to your network. Configure your Mr Beam for your WiFi with WiFi name and password.') }}</p>
                                        <p>{{ _('After that you can access it with any computer (<a href=\"https://find.mr-beam.org\" target=\"_blank\">find.mr-beam.org</a>) that is in the same home network.') }}</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="span6">
                                        <h5>{{ _('Pros / Cons') }}</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Controllable from everywhere in your network') }}</p></li>
                                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Software updates via your secured home network') }}</p></li>
                                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Support tickets can be sent directly from your Mr Beam') }}</p></li>
                                            <li>+ <p>{{ _('Access to the entire Mr Beam Design and Material Store') }}</p></li>
                                            <li>- <p>{{ _('The router must be close enough to the Mr Beam') }}</p></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span12">
                                <div class="connection-wizard__div--notice">
                                    <div class="row-fluid">
                                        <div class="span1">
                                           <span>i</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="span11">
                                            <h4>{{ _('This is how it’s done') }}</h4>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row-fluid">
                                        <div class="span12">
                                            <div id="wizard_welcome_wifi_configuration">
                                                <div data-bind="visible: hasDataLoaded()">
                                                    <div class="pull-right" data-bind="visible: netconnectdViewModel.enableQualitySorting">
                                                        <small>
                                                            {{ _('Sort by') }}: <a href="#" data-bind="click: function() { netconnectdViewModel.listHelper.changeSorting('ssid'); }">{{ _('SSID') }} ({{ _('ascending') }})</a> | <a href="#" data-bind="click: function() { netconnectdViewModel.listHelper.changeSorting('quality'); }">{{ _('Quality') }} ({{ _('descending') }})</a>
                                                        </small>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <table class="table table-striped table-hover table-condensed table-hover" id="">
                                                        <thead>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <th class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_ssid">{{ _('SSID') }}</th>
                                                            <th class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_quality" data-bind="visible: netconnectdViewModel.enableQualitySorting">{{ _('Quality') }}</th>
                                                            <th class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_action">{{ _('Action') }}</th>
                                                        </tr>
                                                        </thead>
                                                        <tbody data-bind="foreach: netconnectdViewModel.listHelper.paginatedItems">
                                                            <tr data-bind="attr: {title: name}">
                                                                <td class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_ssid"><span class="icon-lock" data-bind="invisible: !encrypted"></span> <span data-bind="text: ssid"></span> <small class="muted">({{ _('Address') }}: <span data-bind="text: address"></span>)</small></td>
                                                                <td class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_quality" data-bind="visible: $root.netconnectdViewModel.enableQualitySorting">
                                                                    <div data-bind="css: $root.netconnectdViewModel.signalQuality(quality)" class="signal-bars mt1 sizing-box four-bars">
                                                                        <div class="first-bar bar"></div>
                                                                        <div class="second-bar bar"></div>
                                                                        <div class="third-bar bar"></div>
                                                                        <div class="fourth-bar bar"></div>
                                                                        <div class="fifth-bar bar"></div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </td>
                                                                <td class="settings_plugin_netconnectd_wifis_action">
                                                                    <button class="btn btn-small" data-bind="click: function() { $parent.netconnectdViewModel.configureWifi($data); }, css: {disabled: $root.netconnectdViewModel.working() || $root.netconnectdViewModel.error() || $root.netconnectdViewModel.getEntryId($data) == $root.netconnectdViewModel.statusCurrentWifi()}"><i class="icon-spinner icon-spin" data-bind="visible: $root.netconnectdViewModel.working"></i><i class="icon-signin" data-bind="visible: !$root.netconnectdViewModel.working()"></i> {{ _('Connect') }}</button>
                                                                </td>
                                                            </tr>
                                                        </tbody>
                                                    </table>
                                                </div>
                                                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" data-bind="click: function() { $root.netconnectdViewModel.refresh() }, enable: $root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline() && $root.netconnectdViewModel.status.wifi.present()">{{ _('Refresh') }}</button>
                                                <div>
                                                    <small class="muted">{{ _('netconnectd socket') }}: <span data-bind="text: netconnectdViewModel.settings.plugins.netconnectd.socket"></span></small>
                                                </div>
                                                <div>
                                                    <div><small><a href="#" class="muted" onclick="$(this).children().toggleClass('icon-caret-right icon-caret-down').parent().parent().parent().next().slideToggle('fast')"><i class="icon-caret-right"></i> {{ _('Advanced options') }}</a></small></div>
                                                    <div class="hide row-fluid">
                                                        <button class="btn span6" data-bind="click: function() { if ($root.netconnectdViewModel.apRunning()) { $root.netconnectdViewModel.sendStopAp(); } else { $root.netconnectdViewModel.sendStartAp(); } }, enable: $root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline()"><span data-bind="visible: !$root.netconnectdViewModel.apRunning() && $root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline()">{{ _('Start AP') }}</span><span data-bind="visible: $root.netconnectdViewModel.apRunning() && $root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline()">{{ _('Stop AP') }}</span><span data-bind="visible: !$root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline()">{{ _('Daemon offline') }}</span></button>
                                                        <button class="btn span6" data-bind="click: function() { $root.netconnectdViewModel.sendReset() }, enable: $root.netconnectdViewModel.daemonOnline()">{{ _('Reset daemon') }}</button>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <p>&nbsp;<p/>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row-fluid">
                                        <div class="span12">
                                            <p>{{ _('Select your WiFi network. Then enter the password needed to connect to your regular home network (WiFi) as usual.') }}</p>
                                            <p>{{ _('Make sure your router is nearby and the connection strength to your Mr Beam is strong.') }}</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</div>
